Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}好想拿到内定啊 内定...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}星星学长的话在严冬到来之前肯定会定下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,0:23:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}嗯 星星学长的话肯定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}哟 未来的总理大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,72)}严冬啊...会来吗...
